Clearly, much more than a depiction of an elderly woman having tea on a cloudy day! Have you been to Ottawa? .

Crooks and castles 🏰
•
After navigating our way through a half finished building and climbing up 20 something flights of stairs, we made it onto the roof to be greeted by one of the moodiest sky's I've ever seen over Canada's capital city. Slapped on the telephoto and tried my best to capture it, but you really had to be there. Trust me, it was incredible ☁️
